Client-side files:
payment_form.html: Frontend form for making a payment.
payment_status_integration_example.html: Example frontend page for freelancers to view payment status.
show_payment_status.js: JavaScript to fetch and display payment status on the freelancer side.


Freelancer-side files:
payment_status_integration_example.html: Also used by freelancers to view payment status.
show_payment_status.js: Used to fetch and display payment data.

Backend (server-side) files:
add_payment.php: PHP API endpoint to record payments.
show_payments.php: PHP API endpoint to fetch payment records.
